expand rate matrix for testing status

Source: R/testify.R
testify.Rd

expand rate matrix for testing status

testify(ratemat, params, debug = FALSE, testing_time = NULL)

Arguments

ratemat

original rate matrix
params

parameters
debug

what it sounds like
testing_time

"report" (N and P are counted at the time when individuals move from _n, _p to _u, _t compartments) or "sample" (N and P are counted when individuals move from _u to _n or _p)

Examples

params <- read_params("PHAC_testify.csv")
state <- make_state(params[["N"]],E0=params[["E0"]])
M <- make_ratemat(state,params)
image(M)
